3 2. Density requirements. A municipality shall allow an affordable housing
4 development where multifamily dwellings are allowed to have a dwelling unit density of
5 at least 2 1/2 times the base density that is otherwise allowed in that location and may not
6 require more than 2 off-street parking spaces for every 3 units. The development must be
